# Build context for the Railway Python image (infra/Dockerfile.python). Only the
# Python workspace (services/*, uv.lock, pyproject.toml) is needed — exclude the
# TS/asset trees so the Railway build stays lean. (Vercel builds web separately
# and does not use this file.)
.git
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.venv
.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.turbo
apps
packages
docs
design
*.log
*.png
*.pdf
.DS_Store
